elements.name: E15 - Create member with Invalid Values

steps.name: the user navigates to Ghost at "<GHOST>"
the user logs in using the credentials "<USERNAME>" and "<PASSWORD>"
the user navigates to the members page
the user clicks on the 'New member' link
the user clicks on the 'Save' button
the user should see the message 'Invalid Email.'
the user should see the message 'Note is too long.'
